name: DOOMER BOARDS SPEEDMAPPING SESSION YO
description: So we decided to have a speedmapping session for some reason, which was held during the entire day of 03.12.2017. The participants had a choice of 4 various map themes, meant to be used one-at-a-time: 1. Shiny-ass silver metal space base 2. Hellish converted techbase 3. Marble gothic temple 4. Depiction of some religious plot
